1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,579
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,636
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,637 --> 00:01:03,720
=Episode 7=

17
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:08,948
(Gu Residence)

18
00:01:52,859 --> 00:01:54,179
Save them.

19
00:01:58,380 --> 00:01:59,379
Save them.

20
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,699
The young lady has always been frail.

21
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:06,379
She fell into the water and caught a chill,
and someone even slipped her an aphrodisiac.

22
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:09,179
Moreover, cold has invaded her body,
throwing yin and yang out of balance.

23
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:10,210
Her fever will not subside.

24
00:02:10,210 --> 00:02:12,979
If we can prepare a concoction
to dispel the cold and expel the evil,

25
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:13,940
there may still be hope.

26
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:15,098
But in her condition,

27
00:02:15,099 --> 00:02:16,539
she cannot even take the medicine.

28
00:02:16,659 --> 00:02:18,139
If this continues,

29
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:20,139
I fear she will not last past midnight.

30
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:25,620
Yes.

31
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,300
Official Gu.

32
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:39,539
This time, I will do everything I can
to assist you in investigating the case.

33
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:42,060
Not only for myself,

34
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:45,207
but also for the innocent courtesans.

35
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,060
This

36
00:02:47,099 --> 00:02:48,259
may be a little unsightly,

37
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:50,300
but I made it with my own hands.

38
00:02:50,499 --> 00:02:51,259
It is for you,

39
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:53,099
as a token of my sincerity
in working with you.

40
00:03:11,539 --> 00:03:12,300
Give us the room.

41
00:03:12,499 --> 00:03:13,300
Yes.

42
00:03:50,099 --> 00:03:51,139
Song Zhiyun,

43
00:03:51,779 --> 00:03:53,859
didn't you swear you would be my blade?

44
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:58,419
Then you cannot die.

45
00:04:13,725 --> 00:04:15,849
笙ｪNight rain falls before the courtyard笙ｪ

46
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:20,599
笙ｪIlluminating the partings
of the mortal world笙ｪ

47
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:27,000
笙ｪStrangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid hues笙ｪ

48
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:31,119
笙ｪA sharp arrow pierces through memory笙ｪ

49
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:34,824
笙ｪLonging spreads like ink笙ｪ

50
00:04:34,825 --> 00:04:38,298
笙ｪBeaded curtains divide love and hate
at either end笙ｪ

51
00:04:38,299 --> 00:04:39,260
Cold.

52
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,574
So cold.

53
00:04:44,575 --> 00:04:48,253
笙ｪLove is a word too hard to sever笙ｪ

54
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:52,886
笙ｪPast ties fade like a dream gone cold笙ｪ

55
00:04:52,887 --> 00:04:55,559
笙ｪIn giving all, we found our only joy笙ｪ

56
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:59,199
笙ｪThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms笙ｪ

57
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:02,774
笙ｪOne night of snow
fell wild and restless笙ｪ

58
00:05:02,775 --> 00:05:09,699
笙ｪEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regret笙ｪ

59
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:13,199
笙ｪWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell笙ｪ

60
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:17,279
笙ｪNo more longing will enter my dreams笙ｪ

61
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:23,832
笙ｪWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you笙ｪ

62
00:05:25,419 --> 00:05:26,619
Shameless thing. Wanton woman.

63
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:27,579
Exactly. No shame at all.

64
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:29,819
Shameless, shameless.

65
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,819
Not a shred of decency.

66
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:32,659
-How utterly shameless.
-I am not.

67
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:37,299
I am not.

68
00:05:37,419 --> 00:05:38,900
I did not.

69
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:55,724
笙ｪThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms笙ｪ

70
00:05:55,725 --> 00:05:59,336
笙ｪOne night of snow
fell wild and restless笙ｪ

71
00:05:59,337 --> 00:06:05,858
笙ｪEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regret笙ｪ

72
00:06:05,859 --> 00:06:06,786
I am here.

73
00:06:06,787 --> 00:06:09,861
笙ｪWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell笙ｪ

74
00:06:09,862 --> 00:06:13,799
笙ｪNo more longing will enter my dreams笙ｪ

75
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:20,560
笙ｪWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you笙ｪ

76
00:06:31,299 --> 00:06:32,539
Why are you on my bed?

77
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:50,340
Ungrateful.

78
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:55,260
(Last night...)

79
00:06:55,299 --> 00:06:57,460
(He was the one
who stayed and took care of me.)

80
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:01,179
Thank you for yesterday.

81
00:07:03,299 --> 00:07:05,059
Recover as soon as you can.

82
00:07:05,219 --> 00:07:07,140
That will be thanks enough.

83
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,145
Your fever has broken.

84
00:07:12,179 --> 00:07:13,580
Get some proper rest.

85
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,539
Strange.

86
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:30,099
Why is my heart racing?

87
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:44,200
When I arrived yesterday,

88
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:47,139
it seemed the people at Shengtang Guild
had already caught wind of it.

89
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,460
The place was completely empty.

90
00:07:48,659 --> 00:07:51,738
This morning, the Divine Guard Army
sealed off the entire South Mountain

91
00:07:51,739 --> 00:07:53,298
under the pretext of hunting rebels.

92
00:07:53,299 --> 00:07:54,732
Even the Imperial Guards?

93
00:07:57,539 --> 00:07:59,199
It seems the mastermind

94
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,357
is no ordinary figure.

95
00:08:02,562 --> 00:08:04,706
He should be hidden
within this painting.

96
00:08:12,979 --> 00:08:14,019
This is...

97
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:15,579
An erotic painting.

98
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:17,357
There are animals.

99
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:18,780
Each animal

100
00:08:19,179 --> 00:08:20,098
represents

101
00:08:20,099 --> 00:08:21,939
a powerful figure hiding behind a mask.

102
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:23,986
Their various crimes are depicted here.

103
00:08:23,987 --> 00:08:25,700
This painting

104
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:28,819
is the fatal shackle
binding them together.

105
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:30,140
It is just a pity

106
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:32,339
that their true identities
are not revealed.

107
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:34,060
It is incomplete as evidence.

108
00:08:34,419 --> 00:08:35,499
Sir, look.

109
00:08:35,699 --> 00:08:36,818
There is also a woman here.

110
00:08:36,819 --> 00:08:38,298
(Madam Begonia)

111
00:08:38,299 --> 00:08:39,859
These animals

112
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:41,778
(Madam Begonia)
are all bowing to her.

113
00:08:41,779 --> 00:08:42,818
Could this madam

114
00:08:42,819 --> 00:08:45,460
be mastermind behind Shengtang Guild?

115
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,578
(Madam Begonia)

116
00:08:46,579 --> 00:08:48,060
Madam Begonia?

117
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,058
Is that not the Old Madam?

118
00:08:50,059 --> 00:08:51,107
Insolence!

119
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,739
Forgive me.

120
00:09:04,819 --> 00:09:07,298
Shengtang Guild has always
kept a low profile.

121
00:09:07,299 --> 00:09:08,339
Yet a few days ago,

122
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:12,060
someone dared to sneak in
disguised as a guest and a courtesan.

123
00:09:12,179 --> 00:09:14,424
They not only caused utter chaos,

124
00:09:14,425 --> 00:09:16,720
but also took the Beauty Portrait.

125
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:20,060
Who leaked the information?

126
00:09:20,179 --> 00:09:22,099
That wretched courtesan

127
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:25,920
is Liu Ruyan, who escaped before.

128
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:29,382
She now goes by the name Song Zhiyun.

129
00:09:30,179 --> 00:09:31,058
And now,

130
00:09:31,059 --> 00:09:34,339
she has joined forces
with Gu Chengye of the Imperial Guard.

131
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:36,538
If they uncover anything,

132
00:09:36,539 --> 00:09:39,180
none of you will escape unscathed.

133
00:09:39,419 --> 00:09:43,507
If I find out who among you
tampered with this,

134
00:09:43,779 --> 00:09:45,507
Shengtang Guild

135
00:09:45,579 --> 00:09:47,739
will never spare them.

136
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:58,979
Your injuries have not yet healed.

137
00:09:59,179 --> 00:10:00,540
Why are you pushing yourself again?

138
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:04,458
The innocent woman
we met at Shengtang Guild

139
00:10:04,459 --> 00:10:06,060
was shot dead.

140
00:10:06,539 --> 00:10:08,060
If I had known how to shoot,

141
00:10:08,179 --> 00:10:09,139
perhaps

142
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:10,645
I could have saved her in time.

143
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:14,060
When you shoot an arrow,

144
00:10:14,412 --> 00:10:15,411
your mind must be calm,

145
00:10:15,419 --> 00:10:16,540
your eyes fixed.

146
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:20,420
Aim for vital points
such as the head or chest.

147
00:10:23,612 --> 00:10:27,219
笙ｪEven if I drift
within a darkened whirl笙ｪ

148
00:10:27,499 --> 00:10:31,707
笙ｪKindred souls
meet the light and become one笙ｪ

149
00:10:32,179 --> 00:10:35,778
The spot you just shot is a false death point,
two cun above the Shanzhong acupoint.

150
00:10:35,779 --> 00:10:38,019
At a critical moment,
it can save a life.

151
00:10:39,362 --> 00:10:43,086
笙ｪBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain笙ｪ

152
00:10:43,087 --> 00:10:46,719
笙ｪThe night runs deep like watching eyes笙ｪ

153
00:10:46,737 --> 00:10:48,861
笙ｪWave after wave of sorrow笙ｪ

154
00:10:48,862 --> 00:10:52,324
笙ｪIn exchange, no one will ever know笙ｪ

155
00:10:52,325 --> 00:10:54,820
笙ｪI will wait笙ｪ

156
00:10:58,459 --> 00:11:00,986
Those of Shengtang Guild
bully the weak and fear the strong.

157
00:11:00,987 --> 00:11:02,386
They prey on defenseless women.

158
00:11:02,387 --> 00:11:03,788
Once you learn archery,

159
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:06,139
you can protect yourself.

160
00:11:06,579 --> 00:11:07,619
In the future,

161
00:11:07,900 --> 00:11:09,580
we must eradicate Shengtang Guild

162
00:11:09,819 --> 00:11:11,220
so that women everywhere

163
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,540
will never suffer again.

164
00:11:15,939 --> 00:11:16,658
By the way,

165
00:11:16,659 --> 00:11:18,418
the Beauty Portrait we obtained,

166
00:11:18,419 --> 00:11:19,540
is it truly useful?

167
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,178
I remember,

168
00:11:23,179 --> 00:11:26,357
(Madam Begonia)

169
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:29,420
I saw an inscription
next to the woman in the painting.

170
00:11:29,620 --> 00:11:31,180
Madam Begonia.
